-- EasyJet Cancels Berlin Flights Because of Lack of De-Icing Fluid, DPA Says
-- B y   A n d r e a s   C r e m e r
-- 2010-12-10T07:22:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-10/easyjet-cancels-berlin-flights-because-of-lack-of-de-icing-fluid-dpa-says.html
EasyJet Plc  canceled flights from
Berlin-Schoenefeld this morning because of a lack of de-icing
materials at the airport,  Deutsche Presse-Agentur  reported.  The last flight to be canceled from Schoenefeld is an 8:40
a.m. service to Barcelona, DPA reported, citing no one. Flights
to Schoenefeld from Amsterdam, Paris and Brussels are also
affected by the cancellations, DPA said.  Spokespeople at Schoenefeld airport and EasyJet couldnâ€™t
